{
  "stem": "14613.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It happened because we were one of the first to hear it, being almost at the end.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We heard a tremendous noise emanating from the back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And shortly thereafter, we see huge tanks with a white star painted on the front of the, on the front of the tank.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, the first thing we thought, the Russians are coming from the back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But as they were getting closer to us, we see suddenly a very curious phenomena.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were walking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were on a highway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "On one side of the highway was a field, and on the other side was a forest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we suddenly see the SS people-- the German guard-- running towards the forest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the tanks are opening, the machine guy shooting in the forest after the SS men.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as they are coming closer, some people are sticking out-- their heads are sticking out from the tanks-- and they are waving us, to us, go on the other side.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Go to the fields.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Here, we see there's no more Germans, tanks coming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We start running to the fields.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they're shooting on the forest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then, the hatch, hatch opened in every tank.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they started-- we see here, packages are being thrown from the tanks to us on the field.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then shortly thereafter, we have learned, these are not the Russians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But these are the American troops, and they send-- and they were throwing to us food, canned ration, candies, biscuits.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Everything what they had in the tanks they would throw to us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in a way, this is how I was liberated, on a highway going from Flossenburg to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
